{"tid":1392793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登出名已經係既定事實","createTime":"2019-08-01T00:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:03:39.000Z","uid":131122,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a83d5850da20a42697d57466c55332a375d2d1f6","tid":1392793,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:51:04.000Z","msg":"其實係咪真係有人聽完譚喂豬講野之後仲覺得只要係呢到開post話係香討既人做就呃到共狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本連登呢個朵好大機會連雜總都聽過<br />\n而既然連登係我地既最大同溫層<br />\n又根本改變唔到連登出左名既事實<br />\n咁點解唔嘗試拉更多既人進入呢個同溫層？<br />\n我相信只要肯落街宣傳連登（可以派啲10蚊m記卷），所有有down app既人都會慢慢變黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢樣野應該要等連仔出手<br />\n<br />\n利申：無意係得到連仔批准前做任何連登宣傳行動"},{"pid":"5350afcb7b404a063cc14c3c27bffd65b5514bf4","tid":1392793,"uid":82640,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:53:15.000Z","msg":"香討同BabyKingdom先係大台<br />\n幾次連登掃走哂啲遊行集會post，都咁多人出黎<br />\n仲有媽媽銀髮嗰啲萬人聚集，連登好似事後先有post咁"},{"pid":"8a52351bd4dc813fbc63d6f82dc1541b1725a8b2","tid":1392793,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:27:19.000Z","msg":"連登個個都係小妹<br />\n抗爭會殘，不了"},{"pid":"de3abf00c46610b4c5422e27e4bab8ca02e086ae","tid":1392793,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"係大陸仲上到連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}